task.summary: Added opencv camera view to ImageCaptureActivity
Added ModelPhotoGalleryActivity and Object3DModel class, also added buttons to switch between activities and folder structure to save images.
Fixed GUI Problems in Photo Gallery
Main Menu can call Photo Gallery Now
Now needs 6 images to create Model
Added ability to Open Model and properly exit program.
Added ability to view images in photogalleryactivity.
Fixed mistake in checking number of images.
Improved removeBackground Algorithm, added boundobject and cropimage2
Added rotate image function, and import object functionality
Thumbnails now get titles added to them.
